title: Stevie Ray Vaughan & Double Trouble And Jeff Beck - The Fire
description:
Stevie Ray Vaughan & Double Trouble And Jeff Beck - The Fire Meets The Fury - 1989 Tour Sampler
Label: CBS Records / Epic - ESK 1901
Format: CD, Promo, Limited Edition
Country: US
Released: 1989
Genre: Blues, Rock
Style: Blues Rock, Texas Blues, Hard Rock


A promotional cd release for the joint 1989 tour with Stevie Ray Vaughan & Double Trouble and Jeff Beck with Terry Bozzio and Tony Hymas. 
Rare 16 track Promo-only cd features 8 tracks from each legendary guitarist.


Tracklist:

1. Stand On It - Beck
2. Tightrope - SRV
3. Going Down - Beck
4. Pride And Joy - SRV
5. Guitar Shop - Beck
6. The House Is Rockin' - SRV
7. Blue Wind - Beck
8. Couldn't Stand The Weather -SRV
9. Savoy - Beck
10. Crossfire - SRV
11. Freeway Jam - Beck
12. Look At Little Sister - SRV
13. Superstition - Beck Bogart Appice
14. Superstition - SRV
15. Beck's Bolero - Beck
16. Willie The Wimp -SRV
